    "SUMMARY": "Irfan Peljto (born 18 July 1984) is a Bosnian professional football referee who officiates primarily in the Bosnian Premier League. He has been a FIFA referee since 2015, and is ranked as a UEFA elite category referee.\nPeljto is the only Bosnian referee to have officiated any UEFA Champions League group stage or knockout phase match."
